<plot>This Warners/Vitaphone entry in the Floyd Gibbons "Your True Adventure" series has Gibbons narrating the story of four women playing bridge in a New Jersey home, while the hostess' mother is asleep upstairs. A neighbor's son sees a thief climb the balcony and enter an upstairs window. His mother calls the hostess,tells her of the intruder and advises her to remain calm as the police are on the way.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?395912</url></doc>
